{"id":34528,"date":"2021-07-11T16:08:10","date_gmt":"2021-07-11T16:08:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/care4calais.org\/?p=34528"},"modified":"2022-06-17T08:28:47","modified_gmt":"2022-06-17T08:28:47","slug":"faisals-story","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/care4calais.org\/news\/faisals-story\/","title":{"rendered":"Faisal&#8217;s story"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">This is Faisal. Originally from Yemen, his story is one of the most brutal I have heard.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">He has been in the UK for one year, lives in a hostel, and has no ID. \u201cIt\u2019s hard to feel at home like this\u201d he often said.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Last week Goods For Good donated some Nike clothing to our team in London. Amongst them was this Official England windbreaker which I gave to Faisal as the weather was wet.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Today when I met him he explained that all week people had been talking to him, waving to him , giving thumbs up and high fives when they saw the Three Lions emblem. <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/static.xx.fbcdn.net\/images\/emoji.php\/v9\/t7f\/1\/16\/1f60a.png\" alt=\"\ud83d\ude0a\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" \/><\/span>. In addition to this, Faisal left his phone on a bus and a very kind woman found it and returned it to him.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">\u201cThis week\u201d, he said \u201cI felt good here in the UK\u201d<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">We\u2019ve all heard the phrase \u201c football\u2019s coming home.\u201d Let\u2019s hope England win. If they don\u2019t, well, I\u2019m just as delighted, that thanks to a generous jacket donation, sporting camaraderie and an unknown woman who found his phone, Faisal at last felt at home.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8211; <a class=\"oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb3vyjys rz4wbd8a qt6c0cv9 a8nywdso i1ao9s8h esuyzwwr f1sip0of lzcic4wl gpro0wi8 q66pz984 b1v8xokw\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/matilda.withervelevitch?__cft__[0]=AZUtoiiQHH5jnN92SUEtovfVtCbkiuYQNdDiMwS755byuzTgXuTxzbEUyxXPSVb_wLDYiKlemxutX-Nk38WTKkS9tmmyFh6nn7BUyrLRs5sBrCCKrplDEKTj7EBnvcHekYBnC34MpY5hbrqja6cZHwKLh1isPDRDs6hrucaUKPay3kS_JkOieiHQ3gseo2Cdmeg&amp;__tn__=-]K-R\">Matilda Wither Velevitch<\/a> volunteer<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb3vyjys rz4wbd8a qt6c0cv9 a8nywdso i1ao9s8h esuyzwwr f1sip0of lzcic4wl gpro0wi8 q66pz984 b1v8xokw\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/refugeeswelcome?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUtoiiQHH5jnN92SUEtovfVtCbkiuYQNdDiMwS755byuzTgXuTxzbEUyxXPSVb_wLDYiKlemxutX-Nk38WTKkS9tmmyFh6nn7BUyrLRs5sBrCCKrplDEKTj7EBnvcHekYBnC34MpY5hbrqja6cZHwKLh1isPDRDs6hrucaUKPay3kS_JkOieiHQ3gseo2Cdmeg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#refugeeswelcome<\/a> <a class=\"oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb3vyjys rz4wbd8a qt6c0cv9 a8nywdso i1ao9s8h esuyzwwr f1sip0of lzcic4wl gpro0wi8 q66pz984 b1v8xokw\" tabindex=\"0\" r